'''改革黨'''（{{lang-lv|Reformu partija}}）是[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]的一个已不存在的[[中間偏右|中間偏右]]政黨，由前[[拉脫維亞總統|拉脫維亞總統]][[瓦尔季斯·扎特莱尔斯|瓦尔季斯·扎特莱尔斯]]在2011年7月23日成立，当时取名为'''扎特莱尔斯改革党'''。2012年4月，该党更名为“改革党”。

2011年7月9日，扎特莱尔斯宣布他將在2011年7月23日－[[2011年拉脫維亞議會解散公投|議會解散公投]]當天成立新政黨。<ref name="BalticTimes">{{cite web |url=http://www.baltictimes.com/news/articles/29032/ |title=Latvian political parties undergo major upheaval |date=12 July 2011 |author=TBT Staff |work=[[波羅的海時報|波羅的海時報]] |accessdate=17 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324114539/http://www.baltictimes.com/news/articles/29032/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DelfiRefDayFound">{{cite web |url=http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/referenduma-diena-zatlers-dibinas-reformu-partiju.d?id=39483621 |title=Referenduma dienā Zatlers dibinās 'Reformu partiju' |trans_title=Zatlers will found "Reform party" on the day of the referendum |language=lv |publisher=Delfi |work=[[拉脫維亞通訊社|拉脫維亞通訊社]] |date=8 July 2011 |accessdate=17 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829042826/http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/referenduma-diena-zatlers-dibinas-reformu-partiju.d?id=39483621 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvnet.lv/zinas/latvija/384149-zatlers_dibinas_reformu_partiju |title=Zatlers dibinās "Reformu partiju" |trans_title=Zatlers will found "Reform party" |language=lv |date=9 July 2011 |publisher=TVNET |work=[[拉脫維亞通訊社|拉脫維亞通訊社]]/BNS |accessdate=17 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318033353/http://www.tvnet.lv/zinas/latvija/384149-zatlers_dibinas_reformu_partiju |dead-url=no }}</ref> 扎特莱尔斯改革黨在7月23日成立，扎特莱尔斯以251票贊成2票反對當選黨魁。<ref>[http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/saeima/nodibina-zatlera-reformu-partiju-eksprezidentu-ievel-par-priekssedi-plkst1925.d?id=39734803 Nodibina Zatlera Reformu partiju; eksprezidentu ievēl par priekšsēdi (plkst.22:10) – DELFI]. Delfi.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244782 Apollo – Ziņas: Nodibina jauno Zatlera Reformu partiju; tās logo – bultas sašauts sarkans krusts] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244782 |date=20110917071733 }}. Apollo.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref> 扎特莱尔斯宣布該黨將不會與三個寡頭政治政黨－[[绿党和农民联盟|绿党和农民联盟]]、[[拉脱维亚第一党/拉脱维亚道路|拉脱维亚第一党/拉脱维亚道路]]和[[人民黨_(拉脫維亞)|人民黨]]（People's Party）合作。<ref name="BalticTimes"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/zatlera-partija-nesadarbosies-ar-zzs-lpplc-un-tp.d?id=39485733 |title=Zatlera partija nesadarbosies ar ZZS, LPP/LC un TP |trans_title=Zatlers' party will not cooperate with UGF, LFP/LW and PP |date=9 July 2011 |language=lv |work=[[拉脫維亞通訊社|拉脫維亞通訊社]] |publisher=Delfi |8= |accessdate=17 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711133516/http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/zatlera-partija-nesadarbosies-ar-zzs-lpplc-un-tp.d?id=39485733 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 改革黨成立兩周後，人民黨解散。<ref>{{cite news |title=Kažoka: Zatlera Reformu partijas uzstādījumi līdzīgi Tautas partijai |language=lv |trans_title=Kažoka: Zatlers Reform party's setting is similar to the People's Party |url=http://la.lv/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=320764:kaoka-zatlera-reformu-partijas-uzstdjumi-ldzgi-tautas-partijai&catid=72:politika&Itemid=95 |date=9 July 2011 |newspaper=Latvijas Avīze |agency=LETA |accessdate=22 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328035302/http://la.lv/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=320764:kaoka-zatlera-reformu-partijas-uzstdjumi-ldzgi-tautas-partijai&catid=72:politika&Itemid=95 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

民調顯示約有33%的民眾支持改革黨<ref name="DelfiVote">{{cite web |url=http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/saeima/aptauja-33-gatavi-balsot-par-zatlera-partiju.d?id=39586217 |title=Aptauja: 33% gatavi balsot par Zatlera partiju |trans_title=Poll: 33% are ready to vote for Zatlers' party |language=lv |author=Delfi staff |work=Delfi |date=15 July 2011 |accessdate=17 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829035209/http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/saeima/aptauja-33-gatavi-balsot-par-zatlera-partiju.d?id=39586217 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2011年7月，有17.5%的民眾選擇投票給改革黨<ref>[http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/reitingi-zatlera-partija-noker-sc-vienotibai-un-zzs-butisks-kritums.d?id=39715663 Reitingi: Zatlera partija 'noķer' SC ; 'Vienotībai' un ZZS – būtisks kritums – DELFI] {{Wayback|url=http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/referendums/reitingi-zatlera-partija-noker-sc-vienotibai-un-zzs-butisks-kritums.d?id=39715663 |date=20110812005147 }}. Delfi.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref>，有52%的民眾認為他們能進入國會。<ref>[http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/saeima/aptauja-iedzivotaji-panakumus-arkartas-velesanas-prognoze-sc-vienotibai-un-zatlera-partijai.d?id=39685697 Aptauja: iedzīvotāji panākumus ārkārtas vēlēšanās prognozē SC, 'Vienotībai' un Zatlera partijai – DELFI] {{Wayback|url=http://www.delfi.lv/news/referendums-2011/saeima/aptauja-iedzivotaji-panakumus-arkartas-velesanas-prognoze-sc-vienotibai-un-zatlera-partijai.d?id=39685697 |date=20110922063520 }}. Delfi.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref>

超過1000名民眾申請入黨<ref name="Apollo1000">[http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244294 Apollo – Ziņas: Zatlera Reformu partijā pieteikušies vairāk nekā 1000 cilvēku] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244294 |date=20120323154901 }}. Apollo.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref> {{As of|2011|July|19|}}，該黨核心由10至15名成員組成。<ref>[http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244373 Apollo – Ziņas: Atklāj topošās Zatlera partijas kodolu] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244373 |date=20110722123657 }}. Apollo.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244478 Apollo – Ziņas: Topošās Zatlera partijas kodolā darbojas vairāki uzņēmēji] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apollo.lv/portal/news/articles/244478 |date=20110919092201 }}. Apollo.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref> 該黨起草10項原則<ref name="DelfiRefDayFound"/><ref>[http://valdiszatlers.lv/ Zatlera Reformu partija | Ārkārtas 11. Saeimas vēlēšanas, kandidāti] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110712085838/http://valdiszatlers.lv/ |date=2011-07-12 }}. Valdiszatlers.lv. Retrieved on 19 September 2011.</ref>，將邀請所有入黨者參與討論。<ref name="Apollo1000"/>

[[2011年拉脫維亞議會選舉|2011年拉脫維亞議會選舉]]，改革黨拿下22席，僅次於[[和諧中間聯盟|和諧中間聯盟]]成為第二大黨。該黨同意與[[團結黨_(拉脫維亞)|團結黨]]、[[民族聯盟_(拉脫維亞)|民族聯盟]]組成執政聯盟，[[瓦爾迪斯·_東布羅夫斯基斯|瓦爾迪斯· 東布羅夫斯基斯]]續任[[拉脫維亞總理|拉脫維亞總理]]，[[瓦尔季斯·扎特莱尔斯|瓦尔季斯·扎特莱尔斯]]將角逐[[拉脫維亞議會議長|拉脫維亞議會議長]]寶座。2011年10月17日，札特勒斯未能當選議長，後同意由團結黨[[索薇塔·阿柏提娜|索薇塔·阿柏提娜]]角逐。6名議員後脫黨成為無黨籍。

2015年3月，该党并入“[[团结_(拉脱维亚)|团结]]”党。

